<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Espaço Carol - Home</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Great+Vibes&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@1,600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">

    <style>
        :root {
            --lilas-pastel: #E0BBE4;
            --roxo-pastel-medio: #D1B3FF;
            --roxo-pastel-escuro: #B38BFF;
            --off-white: #FDFDFD; 
            --cinza-texto: #555;
            --branco-puro: #FFFFFF;
        }

        body { font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; background: var(--off-white); margin: 0; color: var(--cinza-texto); text-align: center; display: flex; flex-direction: column; min-height: 100vh; }
        
        header { position: relative; background-image: url("fundo.jpg"); background-size: cover; background-position: center; padding: 100px 20px; color: var(--branco-puro); }
        header::after { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background-color: rgba(74, 20, 140, 0.3); z-index: 1; }
        header > * { position: relative; z-index: 2; }

        h1 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(40px, 8vw, 85px); font-style: italic; color: var(--lilas-pastel); margin: 0; }

        nav { background: var(--branco-puro); padding: 15px; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 1000; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--lilas-pastel); display: flex; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        nav a { text-decoration: none; color: #444; margin: 5px 15px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; cursor: pointer; }
        nav a:hover { color: var(--roxo-pastel-escuro); }

        section { display: none; padding: 60px 20px; flex: 1; animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease; }
        .active { display: block; }
        @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } }

        .container-form { background: var(--branco-puro); max-width: 450px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 30px; border-radius: 25px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); border: 1px solid var(--lilas-pastel); }
        .input-box { margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: left; }
        input, select { width: 100%; padding: 12px; border: 1.5px solid #eee; border-radius: 10px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; }
        
        .checkbox-group { background: #fcf8ff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #eee; }
        .check-item { display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 14px; }

        .btn-acao { background: var(--roxo-pastel-medio); color: white; border: none; padding: 15px; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: 700; width: 100%; cursor: pointer; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .btn-acao:hover { background: var(--roxo-pastel-escuro); }

        footer { padding: 40px 20px; background: #f9f9f9; font-size: 11px; color: var(--roxo-pastel-escuro); font-weight: 700; border-top: 1px solid var(--lilas-pastel); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Espaço Carol</h1>
        <p>Estética & Bem-estar</p>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <a onclick="mostrar('home')">INÍCIO</a>
        <a href="/login">LOGIN / CADASTRO</a>
        <a onclick="mostrar('agendar')">AGENDAR</a>
    </nav>

    <section id="home" class="active">
        <h2>Onde a beleza encontra a lógica.</h2>
        <p>Agende seu horário com praticidade.</p>
        <img src="salao.jpeg" alt="Salão" style="width: 100%; max-width: 400px; border-radius: 20px; margin-top: 20px;">
    </section>

    <section id="agendar">
        <div class="container-form">
            <h2>Novo Agendamento</h2>
            <form action="/agendar" method="POST">
                <div class="input-box">
                    <label>Data</label>
                    <input type="date" name="data" required>
                </div>
                <div class="input-box">
                    <label>Horário</label>
                    <input type="time" name="hora" required>
                </div>
                <div class="input-box">
                    <label>Procedimentos</label>
                    <div class="checkbox-group">
                        <label class="check-item"><input type="checkbox" name="procedimento" value="Corte"> Corte de Cabelo</label>
                        <label class="check-item"><input type="checkbox" name="procedimento" value="Manicure"> Manicure</label>
                        <label class="check-item"><input type="checkbox" name="procedimento" value="Escova"> Escova</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn-acao">Confirmar Horário</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <span>&copy; 2026 ESPAÇO CAROL | Todos os direitos reservados.</span>
    </footer>

    <script>
        function mostrar(id) {
            document.querySelectorAll('section').forEach(s => s.classList.remove('active'));
            document.getElementById(id).classList.add('active');
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>